gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 120, Pistons 118
gameRecap.excerpt: Led by Damian Lillards 34 points (18 in the 4th quarter), the Bucks defeated the Pistons, 120-118. Brook Lopez added 14 points (4-6 3PM), 6 rebounds and four blocks for the Bucks in the victory, while Cade Cunningham tallied 33 points, eight rebounds and eight assists for the Pistons in the losing effort. The Bucks improve to 5-2 on the season, while the Pistons fall to 2-7.
